author: herald.ie
title: Nicole Kidman: 'Put me on I'm a Celeb and I'll win it'
text:
Hollywood star Nicole Kidman says she could easily have won a series of I'm A Celebrity ... Get Me Out Of Here! because she would not mind eating witchetty grubs. Nicole Kidman 05 October 2015 03:00 AM
"Because I'm Australian we're used to that kind of thing and I've even been known to try a witchetty grub," she said.
"I could've gone on I'm A Celebrity and won it. I wouldn't have to be bribed or anything. I would be happy to eat the witchetty grubs."
The 48-year-old star of Moulin Rouge! also revealed that Italy is next on her travel bucket list.
"I still want to go and live in Italy, work on my Italian and become a better cook, because I'm not a good cook," she said.
